     * |    ├── scion-toolkit (git clone git@github.com:SchweizerischeBundesbahnen/scion-toolkit.git)                               |
     * | 2. Run `npm run copy-src` to copy their source into the `src-lib` folder.                                                  |
     * +============================================================================================================================+
     */
